In the feature flag schema, feature name is the `id` of feature flag. For eg, this is the raw "value" of a key-value that represents a feature flag:
```
{
	"id": "TestFeature1",
	"description": null,
	"enabled": true,
	"conditions": {
		"client_filters": []
	}
}
